text:
Transportation: A beer truck moving northward on 7th Avenue. At the right is the publishing plant of Street and Smith, occupying the easterly frontage of the Avenue from W. 15th to 16th Streets.

1938

Alexander Alland

This photo is one of a series that appeared in the published volume "Portrait of N. Y." by Felix Reisenberg and Alex. Alland, IRGV.

Macmillan, pub.
title: Transportation - Beer Turck.
